                    <h3 class="info__title">Probably the best place to enjoy your life</h3>
                    <p class="info__text-2">A wonderful serenity has taken possession of my entire soul, like these sweet mornings of spring which I enjoy with my whole heart. I am alone, and feel the charm of existence in this spot, which was created for the bliss of souls like mine. I am so happy, my dear friend, so absorbed in the exquisite sense of mere tranquil existence. When, while the lovely valley teems with vapour around me, and the meridian sun strikes the upper surface of the impenetrable foliage of my trees, and but a few stray gleams steal into the inner sanctuary.</p>
                    <h4 class="info__title--2">
                        The European languages are members of the same family. Their separate existence is a myth. For science, music, sport, etc, Europe uses the same vocabulary.
                    </h4>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<!-- section-count-to -->
<div class="section-count-to">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xxl-3 col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-12">
                <div class="count-to-1">
                    <h3 class="timer" data-from="0" data-to="350" data-speed="5000" data-refresh-interval="50"></h3>
                    <p>@GetLanguage.Language(lang, "GUESTSTAY")</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xxl-3 col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-12">
                <div class="count-to-1">
                    <h3 class="timer" data-from="0" data-to="@roomShowHomes.Count()" data-speed="5000" data-refresh-interval="50"></h3>
                    <p>@GetLanguage.Language(lang, "room")</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xxl-3 col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-12">
                <div class="count-to-1">
                    <h3 class="timer" data-from="0" data-to="12" data-speed="5000" data-refresh-interval="50"></h3>
                    <p>@GetLanguage.Language(lang, "Awards")</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xxl-3 col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-12">
                <div class="count-to-1">
                    <h3 class="timer" data-from="0" data-to="150" data-speed="5000" data-refresh-interval="50"></h3>
                    <p>@GetLanguage.Language(lang, "Meal served")</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
